<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, August 11 (Xinhua) -- State Secretary of the
Romanian Defense Ministry Constantin Degeratu said today Romania
would further improve military cooperation with China, which is
playing an important role in the world.
</P>
<P>
During a meeting with Zhou Ziyu, Deputy Director of the General
Political Department of the Chinese People's Liberation Army,
Degeratu praised China for its reforms and opening-up practice in
recent years. Because of these, China had become the fastest
growing country in the world, he added.
</P>
