Constanti Dudu Ionescu, another state secretary of the
Romanian Defense Ministry, also held talks today with Zhou on
furthering ties between the two armies.
</P>
<P>
Ionescu said Romanian President Emil Constantinescu would visit
China soon, and this, he believed, would be helpful in the
development of bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
The delegation headed by Zhou arrived here on August 10 for a
five-day visit and is expected to visit Hungary on August 15.
