India's relations with its neighbors. "Our relations with our
neighbors --Bangladesh, Nepal and the Maldives-- have moved on and
are qualitatively very different than they were a year ago."
</P>
<P>
With the South Asian region due to become a free trade area by
the year 2001 as decided at a regional summit in the Maldives in
May, the togetherness of the region would be enhanced, he added.
</P>
