<HEADLINE> Drug Users Increase in Philippines </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, August 12 (Xinhua) -- The number of Filipinos addicted
to drugs is growing rapidly and is now placed at four million, the
official Philippine News Agency (PNA) reported today.
</P>
<P>
From the 250,000 drug addicts in 1980, the number doubled to
500,000 in 1990 and then reached 1.5 million in 1992, the agency
quoted a report from the Dangerous Drugs Board.
</P>
