<P>
Walker's timing was 53.04 seconds, three hundredths of a second
faster than the previous record.
</P>
<P>
Early, the 21-year-old has notched up two silver medals in the
men's 100-meter freestyle and 100-meter backstroke.
</P>
<P>
It was the eighth meet record set in the championships. 
</P>
</TEXT>
