<HEADLINE> Russian Foreign Minister to Visit Georgia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, August 11 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin
telephoned his Georgian counterpart today and said he would send
Foreign Minister Yevgeny Primakov to Tbilisi to help resolve the
dispute over the breakaway province of Abkhazia.
</P>
<P>
