the Foreign Affairs Committee of the Chinese National People's
Congress and a delegation of the International Relations Committee
of the U.S. House of Representatives. Gilman and his delegation
arrived in Beijing Sunday at the invitation of the NPC Foreign
Affairs Committee.
</P>
