SAN JOSE -- Presidents from Central American countries and the
Dominican Republic will meet on August 22 in Managua, Nicaragua to
review the region's economic integration system, the Costa Rican
Foreign Ministry announced.
</P>
<P>
KIEV -- The Ukrainian Cabinet has decided to sell a Soviet
aircraft carrier, the Ukraine National News Agency reported
Monday. The paperwork for the tender of the uncompleted "Varyag"
carrier will be ready by the end of this month. "Varyag," ordered
by the former Soviet navy, was built by the Pontic Navy Yard in
the Black Sea port of Mykolaiv, Ukraine's major shipbuilding
center. 
