<HEADLINE> Show Targets Machinery Sector </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 12 (Xinhua) -- About 220 exhibits from 13
nations will display products and technological advancements in
power transmission and control, fluid power, internal combustion
engines and gas turbines from September 15 to 19 in Beijing,
today's "China Daily" reports.
